text: Poticaw Landing is an unincorporated community in Jackson County, in the U.S. state of Mississippi. ==History== The community takes its name from Poticaw Bayou, which flows past the site. Variant names are "Portico Landing" and "Portigo Landing". ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Mississippi Category:Unincorporated communities in Jackson County, Mississippi
title: Poticaw Landing, Mississippi
